    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>It's about time!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217500/extras/58cd89b23e83b0d773c242cccbf00c89.webp?t=1768327843\" width=512 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A series of storms approaches the Hourglass Isles. Some people need your aid to weather the lightning, waves, and torrential rain, while others would appreciate help in personal quests. Plan your schedule wisely and make the most of your time—can you balance the demands of the archipelago and ensure everyone gets the help they need?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217500/extras/6df58704a5f0c948afd77f74efa7d7d1.poster.avif?t=1768327843\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217500/extras/6df58704a5f0c948afd77f74efa7d7d1.webm?t=1768327843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217500/extras/6df58704a5f0c948afd77f74efa7d7d1.mp4?t=1768327843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217500/extras/c9be92eb12b47ca99f389710aa723014.webp?t=1768327843\" width=512 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plan your days to maximize your impact—choose when and where to lend a hand as you balance the needs of the islanders. Earn renown for your helpful deeds, but timing is everything. Can you navigate optimally, arrive on time, and help everyone in need? Your scheduling skills are the key to success!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217500/extras/b8d36c9cb38f362de08e4a201ff6af15.poster.avif?t=1768327843\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217500/extras/b8d36c9cb38f362de08e4a201ff6af15.webm?t=1768327843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217500/extras/b8d36c9cb38f362de08e4a201ff6af15.mp4?t=1768327843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217500/extras/8870233417c365ccc67d1feb73e877c0.webp?t=1768327843\" width=512 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover hidden paths, secret locations, and new routes as you navigate the Hourglass Isles. Every discovery opens up new opportunities to optimize your travels and complete your schedule more efficiently. Explore to your advantage and make every moment count!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217500/extras/e98adb5a3dc937da196c042d6538afea.avif?t=1768327843\" width=304 height=172 /></span>     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217500/extras/29362c36c4196331c51a173a74801ebd.avif?t=1768327843\" width=304 height=172 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217500/extras/2de90f5cb008597d1f69863737386f30.avif?t=1768327843\" width=304 height=172 /></span>     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217500/extras/5ac6f2936759999af33e8fa11f6b5d5b.avif?t=1768327843\" width=304 height=172 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217500/extras/9aa7159badaf0891e15c5c9e8018c0aa.webp?t=1768327843\" width=512 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hone your planning skills in a fun, interactive way that utilizes familiar and practical scheduling and calendar tools, preparing you for real-life scheduling challenges!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217500/extras/9dd86104dc9f7c147ef08bc569150164.poster.avif?t=1768327843\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217500/extras/9dd86104dc9f7c147ef08bc569150164.webm?t=1768327843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217500/extras/9dd86104dc9f7c147ef08bc569150164.mp4?t=1768327843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
